==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Kirumbo
<hw>Ki*rum"bo</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A
bird of Madagascar (<spn>Leptosomus discolor</spn>), the only living
type of a family allied to the rollers. It has a pair of loral plumes.
The male is glossy green above, with metallic reflections; the female is
spotted with brown and black.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

